#### `PaymentMethodBreakdown`
**Path:** `src/views/components/admin/financeiro/PaymentMethodBreakdown.tsx`

Recharts `PieChart` (donut) + grid de MethodCards.

Props:
```typescript
interface PaymentMethodBreakdownProps {
  data: MethodData[]
  loading: boolean
}
```

---

#### `MethodCard`
**Path:** `src/views/components/admin/financeiro/MethodCard.tsx`

Card individual por método com ícone, valor, percentual, taxa de aprovação.

```typescript
interface MethodCardProps {
  method: "PIX" | "CREDIT_CARD" | "DEBIT_CARD" | "BOLETO" | "CASH"
  gross: number
  count: number
  approvalRate: number
  averageTicket: number
  shareOfRevenue: number
  disabled?: boolean  // true para Boleto e Dinheiro (em breve)
}
```

