### 7.2 ViewModel (Hook)

**Path:** `src/viewmodels/admin/useFinanceiroViewModel.ts`

```typescript
interface FinanceiroViewModel {
  // Estado
  period: DateRange
  granularity: "day" | "week" | "month"
  activeTab: "overview" | "methods" | "transactions"
