### 7.3 Repository / UseCase Necessários

#### Novo: `IFinanceiroRepository`
**Path:** `src/repositories/IFinanceiroRepository.ts`

```typescript
interface IFinanceiroRepository {
  getSummary(startDate: Date, endDate: Date): Promise<FinanceiroSummary>
  getByPeriod(startDate: Date, endDate: Date, granularity: Granularity): Promise<PeriodDataPoint[]>
  getByMethod(startDate: Date, endDate: Date): Promise<MethodData[]>
  getTransactions(filters: TransactionFilters): Promise<PaginatedResult<Transaction>>
  exportTransactions(filters: TransactionFilters): Promise<TransactionExportRow[]>
}
```

#### Implementação: `PrismaFinanceiroRepository`
**Path:** `src/infrastructure/repositories/PrismaFinanceiroRepository.ts`

Implementação com queries Prisma otimizadas usando `groupBy` e `aggregate`.

